This past weekend as our second and last district qualifier, we competed at the WPI event. At the end of the qualifying period we were 5-7 and were picked by alliance 7 captained by Team 5422 Stormgears, and the first pick Team 9644 NEIA Robotics. We unfortunately went 0-2 in the double elimination bracket but we as a team were very proud of the work we have been able to do this season and take home 18 district points, giving us a total of 47 district points over our two qualifiers. In a photo finish we were able to qualify for district championships as the last team to accept the invitation. We are very excited to return to the Big E once again and we have a surprise in store for it. 

Lets just say ***BALL-E*** is a little less lonely as the only robot in the ***467*** shop.


